605
00:43:26,704 --> 00:43:28,984
What are you talking about?

606
00:43:28,984 --> 00:43:31,575
What are you doing?

607
00:43:33,411 --> 00:43:36,413
Don't be rude to our guests.

608
00:43:50,060 --> 00:43:54,194
I didn't think our friendship would end so quickly.

609
00:44:05,042 --> 00:44:08,311
Such a shame, Little Brother Tang.

610
00:44:08,311 --> 00:44:11,549
I actually really do admire you.

611
00:44:11,549 --> 00:44:14,751
But who told you to be Tang Guodong's son?

612
00:44:15,386 --> 00:44:18,255
He stole my girl from me,

613
00:44:18,255 --> 00:44:20,291
killed my child,

614
00:44:20,291 --> 00:44:22,926
he destroyed my family!

615
00:44:29,633 --> 00:44:31,635
There are so many guns here tonight,

616
00:44:31,635 --> 00:44:34,204
it doesn't look like I'll be able to escape today.

617
00:44:35,739 --> 00:44:37,907
But even if I die,

618
00:44:37,907 --> 00:44:39,477
I won't die alone!

619
00:44:39,477 --> 00:44:41,211
Tang Yi!

620
00:44:43,948 --> 00:44:45,148
Tang Yi.

621
00:44:49,853 --> 00:44:53,756
A dutiful son must pay for a father's debt.

622
00:44:53,756 --> 00:44:57,724
Chen Wenhao, he is your son! You can't kill him!

